Title: BTZ Solutions on Codimension-2 Braneworlds
Authors: B. Cuadros-Melgar and E. Papantonopoulos and M. Tsoukalas and V. Zamarias
Abstract: We consider five-dimensional gravity with a Gauss-Bonnet term in the bulk and an induced gravity term on a 2-brane of codimension-2. We show that this system admits BTZ-like black holes on the 2-brane which are extended into the bulk with regular horizons.
